喺香港嘅話，civil會係你嘅best choice <br />\n<br />\n我唔係話mech無用，而係香港呢個地方令到mech人好難發圍，喺外國，mech人玩車玩飛機，做埋火箭，仲有工業可以畀mech人發揮，但香港就咩都無，啲mech人走哂去做冷氣，做bs，就算你好鍾意mech，但你畢業之後，好大機會要面對一個死氣沉沉，毫無創新可言嘅行業，到時你點對得住你張mechanical engineering 嘅degree?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"香港做飛機做死你。人工低行頭窄。"},{"pid":"2bf65b408f15ed2a8debf861f0c53386bc39c355","tid":712902,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"若要生活好, 味撚讀civil 呀, 連登日日loop呢句你仲入唔到腦?"},{"pid":"d255b3e11738b18d4f7db845d9cb8504d9c4bd26","tid":712902,"uid":188,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"萬般皆下品 唯有土木高"},{"pid":"2bad82d499eabada475300f1e73fdaf5a65be2b6","tid":712902,"uid":74259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"grad e 位計<br />\nMe Ee Bse 三個加埋都冇civil多<br />\n但係學位畢業人數就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6edb80f850036f02236fef01d272e391c2861b9","tid":712902,"uid":74259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bad82d499eabada475300f1e73fdaf5a65be2b6","tid":712902,"uid":74259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"grad e 位計<br />\nMe Ee Bse 三個加埋都冇civil多<br />\n但係學位畢業人數就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"civil係淨係civil 仲未計geo同stl <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07469242c4def4d3f7ef87ee74dd15ca4e87722","tid":712902,"uid":126609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:32:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6286f7f39a26e105e4c96bac46c92b0245fb3fb6","tid":712902,"uid":50693,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"hku 讀civil 無得輸"},{"pid":"c6d8436f67e575680370b8cc38b656f49f14367a","tid":712902,"